data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-story colonial-style home located in the highly sought-after area of  breezy point with 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms. As you enter the house, you'll be greeted by cathedral ceilings in the foyer, creating a grand and inviting atmosphere as well a generous sized office making it the perfect space for work or relaxation.The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and elegant granite countertops, making meal preparation a breeze. Bringing you a first floor bedroom with en-suite bathroom perfect for an elderly parent Step outside to the beautiful back deck, where you can enjoy outdoor gatherings and the serene backyard with a generous-sized shed for extra storage.This home comes with a newer roof for peace of mind, and the bathrooms have been tastefully updated, adding a modern touch to this classic colonial style home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home!
